sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SRE
    participant OC as oc CLI
    participant Gather as gather.sh<br/>Entry Point
    participant XksUtil as xks_util.sh<br/>Distro Detection
    participant Common as common.sh<br/>Shared Functions
    participant Components as Component Gather Scripts<br/>(13 scripts, parallel)
    participant LLMD as gather_llmd.sh<br/>xKS Path
    participant Deps as Dependency Scripts<br/>(cert-manager, sail, lws)
    participant Helm as helm CLI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>/must-gather/

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,FS: Flow 1: OpenShift Must-Gather Collection
        User->>OC: oc adm must-gather --image=must-gather:tag
        OC->>Gather: Executes in must-gather pod
        Gather->>Common: source common.sh
        Gather->>XksUtil: source xks_util.sh
        XksUtil->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/config.openshift.io<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>XksUtil: OpenShift detected

        Gather->>K8sAPI: oc adm inspect namespace/redhat-ods-operator<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Gather: Operator namespace resources

        Gather->>K8sAPI: Collect DSCInitialization, DataScienceCluster,<br/>Auth, Monitoring, GatewayConfig CRs
        K8sAPI-->>Gather: Platform-level CRs

        par 13 Component Scripts (parallel)
            Gather->>Components: Dispatch all component gather scripts
            Components->>Common: get_all_namespace(resources)
            Common->>K8sAPI: GET CRDs across all namespaces<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
            K8sAPI-->>Common: Namespace list
            Components->>K8sAPI: oc adm inspect for each namespace<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
            K8sAPI-->>Components: Component CRs + pods + logs + events
        end

        Gather->>Helm: helm get values / helm get manifest
        Helm->>K8sAPI: GET Helm secrets<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Helm: Helm release data
        Helm-->>Gather: Release values and manifests

        Gather->>FS: Write all collected data to /must-gather/
        OC-->>User: Tarball of /must-gather/ directory
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,FS: Flow 2: xKS Kubernetes Job Collection (AKS/EKS/CKS)
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply -f job.yaml<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
        K8sAPI->>Gather: Job pod starts, executes gather.sh

        Gather->>XksUtil: source xks_util.sh
        XksUtil->>K8sAPI: Probe node labels, provider IDs<br/>Auth: must-gather-sa token
        K8sAPI-->>XksUtil: AKS/EKS/CKS detected

        Gather->>LLMD: Dispatch llm-d collection path
        LLMD->>K8sAPI: kubectl get cluster-info, nodes, api-resources<br/>Auth: must-gather-sa token
        K8sAPI-->>LLMD: Cluster metadata

        par Dependency Collection (parallel)
            LLMD->>Deps: cert-manager.sh
            Deps->>K8sAPI: GET Issuer, ClusterIssuer, Certificate CRs
            K8sAPI-->>Deps: cert-manager resources

            LLMD->>Deps: sail.sh
            Deps->>K8sAPI: GET Istio, VirtualService, DestinationRule,<br/>AuthorizationPolicy, PeerAuthentication CRs
            K8sAPI-->>Deps: Istio/Sail resources

            LLMD->>Deps: lws.sh
            Deps->>K8sAPI: GET LeaderWorkerSet CRs
            K8sAPI-->>Deps: LWS resources
        end

        LLMD->>K8sAPI: auto_discover_resources: kubectl api-resources,<br/>GET all namespaced resource types
        K8sAPI-->>LLMD: All discovered resources

        LLMD->>K8sAPI: kubectl logs (current + previous) for all pods<br/>Auth: must-gather-sa token
        K8sAPI-->>LLMD: Pod logs

        LLMD->>Helm: helm get values / helm get manifest
        Helm->>K8sAPI: GET Helm secrets
        K8sAPI-->>Helm: Release data
        Helm-->>LLMD: Helm values

        LLMD->>FS: Write to /tmp/must-gather/
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl cp must-gather-pod:/tmp/must-gather ./
        K8sAPI-->>User: Collected diagnostic data
    end
